column5: Hey guys, anyone know who has minnows up that way. Headed up tomorrow and just got the news the outfitter is without minnows. Thanks, R

I always get mine at Gramp's Place just south of town. Can't imagine they won't have minnows.  Also, depending on what time you're passing through Orillia you can get them at Epp's right on the hwy too.
Gramps, located near Rabbit Lake rd, on Hwy11.
we are leaving for Temagami as well, spoke to Gramps and they have minnows. Where are you staying in Temagami? Bruce's place?
Yes our group will be staying at TAMAR. Are you with Morgan's group?
Great, thanks for the info guys. R
See you at Tamar tomorrow, we are not with Morgan's group.
PLEASE buy them at Gramps!! Don't be bring them up from the Simcoe water shed. We've got enough invasives in Temagami already, we don't need anymore.
